#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/cpu_binding.md:210
msgid ""
"The allocator includes the hidden same-affinity NPU as a candidate in "
"each process, splits the shared extended pool, and then keeps only the "
"visible NPU in the final pool."
msgstr "分配器将隐藏的相同亲和性NPU作为候选包含在每个进程中，拆分共享的扩展池，然后在最终池中仅保留可见的NPU。"

